    "The webhook only serves as a bridge for the connection.",
    "Flask applicationIn this step, we created the Flask application using Python.",
    "This application is responsible for combining the LangChain Agent with the Dialogflow CX agent through the webhook, in order to obtain the F-One Chatbot as a unified entity.",
    "In the case of this project, we created a route method named route/webhook with a POST request to handle all the webhook requests from the Dialogflow CX Agent.",
    "Therefore, whenever a fulfilment is triggered with a webhook, Dialogflow sends a POST HTTPS webhook request to this URL/webhook."
